              </TextRun>
              <TextRun>
                <Value>

Logistics, loading &amp; unloading charges are to be borne by the customer unless specifically mentioned in this Invoice.

Renewed / Open-Box products may have damaged packaging or minor dents/scratches. The customer accepts the product condition as checked &amp; noted in this Invoice. Refunds are not applicable for such cases.

No refunds/replacements will be entertained once the product is accepted. Functional issues (if any) during the warranty period will be resolved either via the brand’s Authorized Service Partner or by Qarmatek directly.</Value>
